Given this political fundraising email, respond with the name of the committee in the disclaimer that begins with Paid for by but does not include Paid for by, the committee address or the treasurer name. If no committee is present, return "None". Do not include any other text, no yapping.
name: CAPT Hung Cao
email: info@hungcaoforva.com
subject: I’m so grateful for you
body: Peter, I am so incredibly grateful for all of your generosity and supportduring our FINAL end-of-month push of the election. We truly would not havegotten this far without you. This grassroots team means everythingto me. Wehave just four more days until Election Day, and with you on my team, I knowwe can win this thing. Now, let’s get to work! In Liberty, CAPT Hung Cao USN(Ret) TEXT HUNG TO 21412 Hung Cao: I’ll get right to the point - the Electionis officially in less than two weeks, so we’re launching an EMERGENCY ELECTIONFUND to make sure we have the resources we need to win. I'm asking for yourhelp today - whether you're able to give $5 or $25 today, any amount isgreatly appreciated. DONATE NOW TO HELP WIN OUR ELECTION & FLIP VIRGINIA REDJOIN TEAM CAO Paid for by Hung Cao for Virginia Use of military rank, jobtitles, and photographs in uniform does not imply endorsement by theDepartment of the Navy or the Department of Defense. Unsubscribe.
